      "content": "it just feels like i'm stuck in a loop. everything is just gray. sometimes i look at his side of the bed and i just think... it would be so much easier if the silence didn't matter anymore. if i didn't have to wake up to this every single day. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
